                        <interp inst="t18420919-name-136" type="given" value="STEPHEN"></interp>STEPHEN SMITH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 254.) I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was twenty yards behind the man when the gentleman laid hold of me.</p>
